{"id": "1413140465733210193", "channel_id": "1413140465733210193", "type": 0, "author_id": "383570112445153281", "author_name": "nuxf", "author_bot": false, "content": "Before I invest more into these characters I want to know if they're worth it. I'm thinking of subbing out Salvador but I don't know who for. also WoD recommendations would be nice because I don't know what to use on faint.", "timestamp": "2025-09-04T12:35:41.911000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1413140466781782087", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2697919, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1413140465733210193/1413140466781782087/image.png?ex=69cd111e&is=69cbbf9e&hm=82c54f27de8a8cfe2f3e9fc9fe9ce1f07aa78aac21d3af48a9c75435f6c26933&"}, {"id": "1413140467482361866", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 668114, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1413140465733210193/1413140467482361866/image.png?ex=69cd111e&is=69cbbf9e&hm=0dc724cbc0bb0426479fb1c540ab83c5816c02500614c9f82660a81f078cd94d&"}, {"id": "1413140468690059354", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2592895, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1413140465733210193/1413140468690059354/image.png?ex=69cd111e&is=69cbbf9e&hm=cdbeb2587cfa22eb7e0cfe37334b57269c1d533bf0ada9bee044a1a9a62ce2e7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413140465733210193", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team Building/Character Help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1413238215178981548", "channel_id": "1413140465733210193", "type": 19, "author_id": "693983290423509042", "author_name": "climbkaly", "author_bot": false, "content": "So this is hard to answer.\n\nBut I'll be candid.\n\nMost don't use Kathi with Caro. \n\nKathi is a powercrept Jenkins. I literally took my Jenkin team swapped out Jenkin for Kathi.\n\nEventually you may want Thais and Faint on a  different team. They are really great units in Caro and worth building.\n\nSo you can keep going as is and maybe swap out Salv with Pickman (coming out in a few days) or pivot your team.\n\nIf pivot, I'd recommend:\n\nKathi / Lily / Horla / Erica or Nautila", "timestamp": "2025-09-04T19:04:07.195000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-04T19:04:46.284000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["383570112445153281"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1413140465733210193", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413140465733210193", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Team Building/Character Help", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747088995811358"]}
